title: 02/12/21 – Hour 2 - The Argument Against Trevor Lawrence. Guest – Buccaneers center A.Q. Shipley
itunes:title: 02/12/21 – Hour 2 - The Argument Against Trevor Lawrence. Guest – Buccaneers center A.Q. Shipley
description:
Jason Smith and Doug Gottlieb sit in for Dan Patrick and further their discussion on the release of J.J. Watt by the Houston Texans. They talk about Trevor Lawrence's pro day and question if there's any scenario where Urban Meyer and the Jaguars pass on the former Clemson QB. Plus, Super Bowl LV champion and Tampa Bay Buccaneers center A.Q. Shipley stops by to share what it was like to win a title alongside Tom Brady!
